lead_paragraph: Deliveries are a crucial metric of performance for the luxury electric vehicle manufacturer, which had missed these targets in the previous two quarters.

headline.print_headline: Tesla Closer to Its Goal With a Rise in Deliveries
headline.main: Tesla Moves Closer to Target With 70 Percent Delivery Increase

snippet: Deliveries are a crucial metric of performance for the luxury electric vehicle manufacturer, which had missed these targets in the previous two quarters....
abstract: Tesla Motors reports third-quarter deliveries rose 70 percent to 24,500 cars; announcement confirms firm is on track for meeting 50,000-vehicle target for second half of 2016, and improves its chances of raising capital for future projects.
